{% submission %}

{% submission-part type="problem" %}

Behavior management, parent contact, sign-ups for conferences all in one app

{% /submission-part %}

{% submission-part type="proposed-solution" %}

I would be interested in a user-friendly, gamified application that allows students to engage through personalized avatars while tracking behavior and progress. Ideally, the platform would also integrate parent teacher sign ups and communication features into a single system. Since students do not have individual computer access, the application would need to support projection for whole-class use.

{% /submission-part %}

